high_descs: Turn around and go to the small desk with the lamp on it.
Pick up the pen to the left of the clock nearest to you.
Turn around, turn left and then face the large desk against the wall on the right.
Open the top desk drawer and put the pen inside the drawer.
Turn right and get closer to the large desk.
Pick up the pen on this large desk.
Back away from the desk to face the desk drawers.
Place this pen inside the top desk drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move the pens from the small desk and the large desk into the top large desk drawer.
